title: Top Floor 2 Bedroom Beauty East Humboldt Park
posting_body: ['946 N California Ave, 3F, Chicago, IL 60622-4402', 'Top Floor 2 Bedroom Beauty East Humboldt Park', 'Come check out this great vintage apartment with modern upgrades!', 'Beautiful hardwood floors throughout.', 'Great living area with loads of natural light.', 'Spacious kitchen includes dishwasher.', 'Updated bathroom with spa-like shower.', '1 bedroom includes closet, 2nd room can easily be a den or office.', 'Central Heat and AC.', 'Shared laundry in building.', 'Pet friendly, with some few breed restrictions.', 'Vibrant intersection with popular restaurants, cafes, bakeries, plant stores, shops and more!', 'Walking distance to the wonderful Humboldt Park and CTA bus transportation.', 'No security deposit required.', 'Non-refundable admin fee of $500.', '$250 per pet fee.', 'Available 8/1.']
